Model.ScoreBoard

Class ScoreBoardCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.ScoreBoard.ScoreBoardCell

  • public class ScoreBoardCell
extends java.lang.Object
    ScoreBoardCell is a class representing a single cell of a ScoreBoard. It may be empty, crossed out or contain a number.
    Author:
    Marianna
